own-chat-intro: ChatGPT is gradually becoming a powerful tool for improving productivity, and using this AI tool effectively can greatly enhance our work efficiency. In order to allow more people (possibly non-programmers) to use ChatGPT better and more conveniently, I have developed OwnChat as a tool.
feature-1-desc: For a single API key, it can allow multiple team members to use it safely.
feature-2-desc: Supports multiple platforms including Web, Desktop, and Mobile.
feature-3-desc: Our servers are deployed in regions where OpenAI API is accessible, thus all clients can use our service without the need for a VPN.
feature-4-desc: one-click sharing of your chat records
feature-5-desc: More elegant interface design and interaction.
about-maker-2: I become a full-time independent developer since this year(2023), I started OwnChat as a passion project. There's no massive team, no investors looking for growth at any cost, just me, running a sustainable business.
